        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段反彈 恒指回升169點報25999點 小米逆市低開0.05%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英偉達上季業績與今季指引均超預期，帶動外圍股市回升，港股亦未有例外，甫開市即逼近二萬六關口。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：英偉達官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250715_FI_source-web_Nvidia-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：英偉達官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250715_FI_source-web_Nvidia-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：英偉達官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數開市報25999點，升169點或0.65%。恒生科技指數開報5646點，升39點或0.7%；國企指數以9203點開市，升52點或0.57%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股普遍造好，阿里巴巴(09988)開報158.3元，升1.22%；騰訊(00700)開報626.5元，升0.64%；美團(03690)開報98.95元，升0.97%；京東(09618)開報113.5元，暫時無升跌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250514_FI_source-web_01810-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250514_FI_source-web_01810-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：小米官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">昨天拖大市後腿的小米(01810)，今早進一步低開0.05%，報38.8元。兩大國際金融股則造好，滙控(00005)開報108元，升0.19%；友邦(01299)開報79.2元，升1.6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">芯片股跟漲，中芯國際(00981)開報74.6元，升2.19%；華虹半導體(01347)開報83元，升3.17%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">剛派成績表的業績股，今早個別發展。聯想(00992)績後升2.49%，報9.87元；快手(01024)開報65.1元，升2.52%。金山軟件(03888)開報30元，逆市跌2.34%；同系金山雲(03896)開報6.2元，漲4.2%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15441137-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%88-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%9b%9e%e5%8d%87169%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125999%e9%bb%9e-%e5%b0%8f%e7%b1%b3%e9%80%86%e5%b8%82%e4%bd%8e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-20 09:30:38",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
